                            <li>Discover your personality type</li>
                            <li>How romantic are you?</li>
                            <li>Which Johhny Depp movie would you exist in?</li>
                            <li>Are you a bridezilla?</li>
                            <li>Which magical power best suits you?</li>
                            <li>How Texas are you?</li>
                            <li>What kind of traveller are you?</li>
                            <li>How well do you know poker?</li>
                            <li>How crazy are you?</li>
                            <li>How smart are you with money?</li>
                            <li>What will you die from? </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
